WEBVTT

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:04.733
you

00:00:05.466 --> 00:00:06.733
Can you do me a favor?

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:07.900
Yes

00:00:08.666 --> 00:00:10.266
You want me to help the Jiang family

00:00:12.333 --> 00:00:14.800
It was Li Zhu who liked him so much

00:00:15.766 --> 00:00:17.766
You weren't that interested in me back then

00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:22.133
Because you left without saying goodbye

00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:24.800
If he hadn't been by my side for the past three years

00:00:24.900 --> 00:00:26.066
I've gone crazy

00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:27.700
I can tie

00:00:28.700 --> 00:00:29.900
But there is one condition

00:00:32.166 --> 00:00:33.133
What kind of condition?

00:00:33.533 --> 00:00:34.533
We get married

00:00:35.366 --> 00:00:39.700
Marriage is what you like, isn't it Yu Qianyin?

00:00:39.966 --> 00:00:41.466
Leave this alone

00:00:41.733 --> 00:00:42.766
Just say no.

00:00:45.666 --> 00:00:46.933
No need for Mr. Lu to fly

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:49.933
I will solve the matter of the Jiang family by myself

00:00:51.400 --> 00:00:54.166
Master Jiang, you said it yourself

00:00:54.266 --> 00:00:55.866
He has the right to choose

00:00:56.533 --> 00:00:59.466
How do you know if he volunteered?